peopleAlsoAsk.question: What is considered a vintage Christmas ornament?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Vintage Christmas ornaments are technically just ornaments that come from an earlier generation. Antique ornaments, on the other hand, are generally regarded as being over 100 years old. Often, people interchange the terms “vintage” and “antique” to refer to older ornaments.
